The Akarigbo of Remoland, Oba Babatunde Adewale Ajayi has pledged his kingdom’s support for the Valuejet 50km Remo Ultra Race, which has been scheduled to hold in Sagamu, Ogun State on December 7, 2019. The post Remo monarch pledges support for 50km Ultra Race appeared first on The Guardian Nigeria News – Nigeria and World News. Source: Guardian